it `9afd1aae4d`, and validate the test updates plus the new `metadata/org.seleniumhq.selenium/selenium-support/4.20.0/reachability-metadata.json`.\n2. Re-run `./gradlew test -Pcoordinates=org.seleniumhq.selenium:selenium-support:4.20.0` on that branch and regenerate stats/coverage for `4.20.0`.\n3. If the rerun is green, land the preserved fix and separately investigate why the workflow marked the run as failed after producing a passing candidate."}}
